<item>
            <title>[LU-4802] Some sanity test should create single stripe directory before we support cross-MDT operation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4802</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some sanity tests(39b, 162, 164) use test_mkdir to create multiple striped directory, but corss-MDT link and rename are not permitted under striped directory. These tests should be changed to create non-striped directories by using:   test_mkdir -c1 $DIR/$tdir&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
